            <abstract>
                <p>Miracle of <persName ref="PRS4377Gabriel"/> concerning a sorcerer named ʾAbrāsit, who lived in the king’s palace.
                    According to the edition of 
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Makweriya1976DersanaGabriel"/><citedRange unit="page">122–127</citedRange></bibl>, it forms
                    part of the monthly reading for the 19th of Maggābit in the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7815DersanaGa"/>.
                    It is also atttested as part of the Homily of <persName ref="PRS3828Epiphani">Epiphanius of Cyprus</persName> in 
                    honour of <persName ref="PRS4585Georgeo">St George</persName> for <date ref="ethiocal:Miyazya19">19 Miyāzyā</date>
                    in <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet149"/>.</p>
            </abstract>
